seo: 致远OA,任意文件读取,漏洞检测,Seeyon,wpsAssistServlet
summary: 检测致远OA系统中的wpsAssistServlet接口是否存在任意文件读取漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞下载服务器上的敏感文件。
summary_en: Detect arbitrary file read vulnerabilities in the wpsAssistServlet interface of Seeyon OA system. Attackers may exploit this vulnerability to download sensitive files from the server.
